data.description: Welcome home to this spacious newly updated, move in ready gem located in sunny Holiday, Fl. NO HOA OR CDD FEES! 4 BEDROOMS & 1 BONUS ROOMS! This unique property has AMPLE room to cater to any of your families needs! This home features a split floor plan with two generously sized bedrooms and bathrooms on one side and 2 bedroom with 1 additional bonus room adjacent. The possibilities are endless! Think of a home office, a nursery, workout room, man cave, teenage loft and more! The home also has an oversized backyard with opportunity  to put a pool, garden or your own personal oasis. This well-kept home is perfect for entertaining family and friends! Conveniently located near Tampa Bay, Clearwater, award winning beaches, golf courses, esqueset dining, shopping, sponge docks in Tarpon Springs, hospitals, shopping centers and more!
